### Get a user

```
Example Request
```

```shell
curl "https://api.example.org/v3/users/[guid]" \
  -X GET \
  -H "Authorization: bearer [token]"
```

```
Example Response
```

```http
HTTP/1.1 200 OK
Content-Type: application/json

<%= yield_content :single_user %>
```

#### Definition
`GET /v3/users/:guid`

#### Permitted roles
 |
--- | ---
Admin |
Admin Read-Only |

**Note:** A user can always see themselves with this endpoint, regardless of role.